<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="5" />Et ensuite je te dirai ce qu'<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x3 0xcd00 0x4 0x69 0x6c 0x8 0x65 0x6c 0x6c 0x65 0x0" /> m'a
