	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Comme on dit,<20_2 arg="2" /> c'est<delay8 /> l'intention<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /> qui
