	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Mais trop!<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 /> Allez, je vais <anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />lui prendre
