<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Mais au fait, <delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />,<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />si t'as envie de l'utiliser aussi, te
